# 📁 Year Tracker — File Structure

year-tracker/
│
├── index.html        ← Main HTML structure
├── style.css         ← All styling + animations
├── script.js         ← All JS logic + PWA register
├── manifest.json     ← PWA config (name, icons, theme)
├── sw.js             ← Service Worker (offline support)
│
└── icons/
    ├── icon-192.png  ← App icon (192×192 px)
    └── icon-512.png  ← App icon (512×512 px)


## 🚀 Deploy on GitHub Pages

1. Create repo: akgtrunner.github.io
2. Upload all files (keep folder structure)
3. Go to Settings → Pages → Enable
4. Live at: https://akgtrunner.github.io

## 📲 Install as App on Phone

### Android (Chrome):
1. Open website in Chrome
2. Tap 3-dot menu → "Add to Home Screen"
3. Tap Install ✅

### iPhone (Safari):
1. Open website in Safari
2. Tap Share button (box with arrow)
3. Tap "Add to Home Screen"
4. Tap Add ✅

## 🎨 Icons kaise banao (Free)

Go to: https://realfavicongenerator.net
- Upload any image
- Download icon pack
- Put icon-192.png and icon-512.png in /icons/ folder